-- India's Inflation May Slow to About 5% by End of March, Mukherjee Predicts
-- Kartik Goyal
-- 2010-06-22T03:54:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/india-s-inflation-may-slow-to-about-5-by-end-of-march-mukherjee-predicts.html

          
          
             India’s inflation may slow to about
5 percent by March 31, Finance Minister Pranab Mukherjee said in
a speech at the Institute of International Finance in Washington
yesterday. Mukherjee’s speech was posted on the website of the
Indian embassy in Washington.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
